37
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:30,550
Brother has not come back until now. When he comes back, I'll eat with him.

38
00:05:30,550 --> 00:05:35,400
Fei'er, you eat with me. When your brother works, there is no end.

39
00:05:35,400 --> 00:05:37,700
Who knows what time he'll be back?

40
00:05:37,700 --> 00:05:42,280
Later, let Mrs Li heat up some rice for him.

41
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:45,370
No worries. I am not hungry yet. You eat first.

42
00:05:45,370 --> 00:05:47,750
Madam, you just eat first.

43
00:05:47,750 --> 00:05:51,510
Miss and Mister have a strong sibling bond.

44
00:05:51,510 --> 00:05:54,490
When Mister drinks hot soup, Miss drinks hot soup too.

45
00:05:54,490 --> 00:05:57,430
When Mister eats cold rice, Miss eats with him.

46
00:05:57,430 --> 00:06:01,430
They go through thick and thin together.

47
