56
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:32,130
I'll go out first.

57
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:37,660
<i>Huzhou Jiang Residence</i>

58
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:42,180
Young Master.

59
00:06:44,790 --> 00:06:49,570
Brother, you only came back now? You have not eaten dinner right? I will bring it to you.

60
00:06:49,570 --> 00:06:52,400
There is no need. I have no appetite.

61
00:07:03,090 --> 00:07:05,370
-Brother
-Come in.

62
00:07:05,370 --> 00:07:10,030
I cooked some porridge for you. No matter what, you should still eat something.

63
00:07:10,030 --> 00:07:13,300
If this carries on, how can your body take it?

64
00:07:13,300 --> 00:07:15,890
Okay, just put it here.

65
00:07:17,180 --> 00:07:18,820
Here.

66
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:25,520
