-Yes.

71
00:07:39,150 --> 00:07:43,800
I heard that there was an accident on the way to Huzhou. It was unintentional.

72
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:46,950
I will meet him again in the next few days.

73
00:07:50,060 --> 00:07:54,500
Alright. Fei Fei, have a early rest. It is late already.

74
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:57,570
Okay. Then you rest early too.

75
00:07:57,570 --> 00:07:59,430
Got it.

76
00:08:09,590 --> 00:08:11,770
If she suddenly has something going on,

77
00:08:11,770 --> 00:08:15,070
it is not standing me up right?

78
00:08:15,070 --> 00:08:17,060
Quickly say yes.

79
00:08:52,310 --> 00:08:54,870
