84
00:09:08,260 --> 00:09:12,000
You can take medicine. If you are sick, you don't have to bear with it.

85
00:09:13,130 --> 00:09:15,190
<i>May Buddha protect us.</i>

86
00:09:19,910 --> 00:09:21,710
Go tomorrow.

87
00:09:33,700 --> 00:09:36,800
<i>Huzhou Newspaper</i>
<i>Died on his birthday: Boss of Ling Long passed away yesterday.</i>

88
00:09:37,710 --> 00:09:40,070
Wu Hong Da is dead.

89
00:09:40,070 --> 00:09:42,720
We only just began a little with our revenge plan.

90
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:45,050
He then suddenly died.

91
00:09:45,050 --> 00:09:48,930
Could it be that this is retribution?

92
00:09:48,930 --> 00:09:52,860
Brother, then our plan to swallow Ling Long

93
00:09:52,860 --> 00:09:54,740
does it still have to progress accordingly?

94
00:09:54,740 --> 00:09:57,480
Did Wu Hong Da, after forcing our father to die,

95
00:09:57,510 --> 00:10:00,480
let Ling Long go so easily?

96
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:02,720
Everything progresses according to the plan.

97
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:06,110
Without Wu Hong Da, this obstruction, our plan

98
00:10:06,110 --> 00:10:08,930
will progress faster and more smoothly.

99
00:10:12,910 --> 00:10:14,620
<i>Return our money.</i>

100
00:10:14,620 --> 00:10:16,290
<i>Return our money. Return it!</i>

101
00:10:16,290 --> 00:10:17,900
Everyone calm down and listen to me.

102
00:10:17,900 --> 00:10:21,310
I am Wu Hong Da's eldest daughter, Wu Cai Hong. This situation is..

103
00:10:21,310 --> 00:10:24,680
What is there to explain? Aren't the facts in front of us?

104
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:27,370
Yes. I've heard for a while now that Ling Long is no longer profitable!

105
00:10:27,370 --> 00:10:29,440
In the past, we gave Master Wu some face

106
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:31,610
so we didn't ask for payment.

107
00:10:31,610 --> 00:10:34,970
Now that the rats have left this sinking ship,
what will you use to pay us back?

108
00:10:34,970 --> 00:10:37,510
<i>Yeah! Return our money!</i>

109
00:10:37,510 --> 00:10:39,930
<i>-Return our money now!</i>
-Let me tell you guys...
-Return the money to us now!

110
00:10:39,930 --> 00:10:42,900
Your Ling Long still owes me half a year's payment for goods!

111
00:10:42,900 --> 00:10:46,730
In order to build a new workshop, Ling Long
still owes us several thousand taels!

112
00:10:46,730 --> 00:10:48,280
<i>-Give us back our money now! Exactly!
-Return our money! Return our money!</i>

113
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:49,800
<i>Give us back our money! It's our money!</i>

114
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:53,390
-Don't worry, everyone,
<i>-Give us back our money!</i>
-Ling Long has money.

115
00:10:53,390 --> 00:10:57,290
It's just that some of it is at the An Yuan Trading Company in Shanghai. It will mature very soon.

116
00:10:57,290 --> 00:10:59,410
-When that time comes, then we can give you your money back.
-Only a ghost would believe you!

117
00:10:59,410 --> 00:11:01,810
I sent someone to Shanghai to inquire about this!

118
00:11:01,810 --> 00:11:04,420
There never was an An Yuan Trading Company!

119
00:11:04,420 --> 00:11:07,570
Ling Long's money has been scammed completely gone!

120
00:11:07,570 --> 00:11:09,750
<i>Return the money! Return the money!</i>

121
00:11:09,750 --> 00:11:14,440
-It's awful! Old Cai is gone - Ling Long's accountant Old Cai has run off!
-What? Run off?

122
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:17,380
If we can't get the money back, let's check the warehouse

123
00:11:17,380 --> 00:11:19,850
to see if there's anything of value in there.
Take as much stuff as they have there.

124
00:11:19,850 --> 00:11:21,350
<i>-Hurry!</i>
-Don't!

125
00:11:21,350 --> 00:11:23,010
<i>-Go in and grab stuff!</i>
-Everyone!

126
00:11:23,010 --> 00:11:25,060
-Everyone, listen to me!
<i>-Hurry, let's go!</i>

127
00:11:25,060 --> 00:11:26,540
Don't!

128
00:11:26,540 --> 00:11:28,270
<i>-Take as much as there is to take!</i>
-Just a minute!
<i>-Exactly!</i>

129
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:29,660
<i>Take it. Take all of it!</i>

130
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:31,490
What are you guys doing?!

131
00:11:31,490 --> 00:11:33,400
<i>Quickly grab it! Quickly get out of the way!</i>

132
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:35,830
You guys put it down, let go!

133
00:11:35,830 --> 00:11:38,070
<i>-Go over there!</i>
-Don't take anything!

134
00:11:38,070 --> 00:11:40,230
<i>-Take them all!</i>
-Please, I'm begging you!
-Move!

135
00:11:40,230 --> 00:11:42,550
Don't take these!

136
00:11:42,550 --> 00:11:45,200
-Let go!
<i>-Get out of the way! Go!</i>

137
00:11:55,370 --> 00:11:57,080
Cai Hong,

138
00:11:57,080 --> 00:11:58,820
are you alright?

139
00:11:58,820 --> 00:12:00,260
Don't be afraid.

140
00:12:00,260 --> 00:12:02,800
No matter what happens, I'll always be with you.

141
00:12:03,990 --> 00:12:06,550
Secretary Zhou! Secretary Zhou!

142
00:12:06,550 --> 00:12:08,830
Secretary Zhou, come here!

143
00:12:10,290 --> 00:12:12,310
The Xiang Fa Dyeing Factory is
scooping up Ling Long's workers right now.

144
00:12:12,310 --> 00:12:14,050
It seems like they will give workers with experience like us

145
00:12:14,050 --> 00:12:16,850
an increase of one percent in wages. Let's go together.

146
00:12:16,850 --> 00:12:19,070
If you want to go, then go by yourself!

147
00:12:29,130 --> 00:12:32,450
-If you kick us out...
-Quickly get out!
-Where will we live?

148
00:12:32,450 --> 00:12:35,390
-This is going too far!
-Go, drive them out!
-Hurry up and get lost!

149
00:12:35,390 --> 00:12:37,740
-Stop!
-Aunt!
-What are you guys doing?!

150
00:12:37,740 --> 00:12:41,410
Shao Tian! Cai Yun. They said that Ling Long
borrowed 50,000 taels.

151
00:12:41,410 --> 00:12:43,000
50,000 taels?!

152
00:12:43,000 --> 00:12:46,890
Yes. This sum of money was due last month.

153
00:12:46,890 --> 00:12:50,110
Look clearly. It's written in black and white.

154
00:12:50,110 --> 00:12:54,360
There is Boss Wu's genuine signature on here.

155
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:57,860
It is indeed Boss Wu's genuine signature. So it shouldn't be a fake.

156
00:12:57,860 --> 00:13:01,090
The loan agreement said that if this amount is not paid back before the due date,

157
00:13:01,090 --> 00:13:04,310
then we can take the Wu mansion as payment.
We came here to collect the house.

158
00:13:04,310 --> 00:13:07,330
-Everyone, can you extend the deadline a few days?
-Yes, can you extend the deadline a few days?

159
00:13:07,330 --> 00:13:10,200
I will definitely think of a way to raise money
to the best of my abilities.

160
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:13,800
Zhou, I don't know what your background is.

161
00:13:13,800 --> 00:13:17,340
Even Wu Hong Da himself couldn't solve this mess.
And we're supposed to count on you?!

162
00:13:17,340 --> 00:13:20,590
You're like a toad wanting to ascend into the sky.
Don't kid yourself!

163
00:13:20,590 --> 00:13:23,430
Enter the house! Go. Go.

164
00:13:23,430 --> 00:13:26,640
You can't do this! Don't close the door!

165
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:29,740
Open the door! Hurry up and open the door!

166
00:13:29,740 --> 00:13:31,010
Hurry up and open the door! This is our home!

167
00:13:31,010 --> 00:13:32,980
What reason do you guys have to kick us out?!

168
00:13:32,980 --> 00:13:35,410
Yes! Hurry up and open the door!

169
00:13:35,410 --> 00:13:37,980
-Madam, what should we do now?!
-Open the door!

170
00:13:37,980 --> 00:13:40,970
How would I know what to do?!

171
00:13:40,970 --> 00:13:43,090
Master,

172
00:13:43,090 --> 00:13:44,870
it hasn't been long since you died,

173
00:13:44,870 --> 00:13:48,670
and these people just bully us like this!

174
00:13:48,670 --> 00:13:50,390
-Madam!
-Mom!

175
00:13:50,390 --> 00:13:52,310
<i>Wu Cai Hong...</i>

176
00:13:52,310 --> 00:13:54,790
<i>you have to pull yourself together.</i>

177
00:13:54,790 --> 00:13:56,940
<i>Starting today,</i>

178
00:13:56,940 --> 00:14:00,690
<i>-you will take father's place and support this family.</i>
-Open the door! Open the door!

179
00:14:00,690 --> 00:14:03,960
<i>Protect your sister and aunt well.</i>

180
00:14:45,130 --> 00:14:47,590
We're here. This is it.

181
00:14:53,550 --> 00:14:55,260
Come in.

182
00:14:57,640 --> 00:15:00,370
Mom, go. Let's go in.

183
00:15:00,370 --> 00:15:02,600
Go.

184
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:06,750
Take a look. This is the house you wanted to rent.

185
00:15:20,340 --> 00:15:22,810
-It's nothing. It's nothing.
-Are you alright?

186
00:15:22,810 --> 00:15:26,680
This has fallen into disrepair for a while.
It'll be fine once I go find a carpenter to fix it.

187
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:29,580
What kind of a place is this?!
How can it be so messy?!

188
00:15:29,580 --> 00:15:31,530
The warehouse in our previous Wu residence

189
00:15:31,530 --> 00:15:33,950
was way tidier than this place.

190
00:15:33,950 --> 00:15:36,970
I'm telling you, no one has lived in this place for a long time.

191
00:15:36,970 --> 00:15:40,350
Also, I'll clean the place up before you move in.

192
00:15:40,350 --> 00:15:44,110
Yes. I think this place is alright actually.

193
00:15:44,110 --> 00:15:46,900
Then if you feel this place isn't bad,

194
00:15:46,900 --> 00:15:51,090
did you want to pay this month's rent first?

195
00:15:56,930 --> 00:15:59,340
- Here.
- All right.

196
00:16:00,190 --> 00:16:03,870
Everyone, since you'll be busy, I won't disturb you.

197
00:16:06,710 --> 00:16:10,460
Brother Shao Tian, sorry for troubling you again.

198
00:16:10,460 --> 00:16:13,720
It should be me who apologizes, Cai Hong.

199
00:16:13,720 --> 00:16:17,040
Right now, there really is no other way.
You guys will have to live in such a simple and crude house.

200
00:16:17,040 --> 00:16:19,540
At present, I can only do this much with my abilities.

201
00:16:19,540 --> 00:16:23,350
However, trust me. I definitely won't let you
live here for too long.

202
00:16:24,510 --> 00:16:27,320
Brother Shao Tian, luckily we have you. If it weren't for you,

203
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:29,800
our family would already be living on the streets.

204
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:32,750
We won't be living on the streets. No matter how big a house is,

205
00:16:32,750 --> 00:16:34,620
in the end, it's just a shelter from wind and rain.

206
00:16:34,620 --> 00:16:38,560
The most important thing right now
is that our whole family is together.

207
00:16:39,580 --> 00:16:43,640
Cai Hong, I really won't let you live in this place

208
00:16:43,640 --> 00:16:48,190
for too long. Sooner or later, there will be a day

209
00:16:48,190 --> 00:16:51,400
where I can definitely let you live in a mansion again.

210
00:16:52,890 --> 00:16:55,660
Brother Shao Tian, you treat my sister so well.
I really admire her.

211
00:16:55,660 --> 00:16:57,240
-Admire what?
-Mom!

212
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:59,850
Silly girl. You need to find someone with a rich family

213
00:16:59,850 --> 00:17:02,110
and take me away from this terrible place as soon as possible.

214
00:17:02,110 --> 00:17:04,860
-This is what is admirable.
-What are you talking about?

215
00:17:04,860 --> 00:17:06,600
It's really dirty here.

216
00:17:06,600 --> 00:17:09,590
Shouldn't it be cleaned?

217
00:17:09,590 --> 00:17:11,880
-I'll do it.
-I'll go with you.

218
00:17:11,880 --> 00:17:13,780
I'll come too.

219
00:17:13,780 --> 00:17:16,650
What do you mean you're going?
You'll get yourself dirty.

220
00:17:16,650 --> 00:17:18,400
Honestly...

221
00:17:32,330 --> 00:17:36,090
Brother Shao Tian. It was really troublesome for you today.

222
00:17:36,090 --> 00:17:38,440
Cai Hong, don't always view me as an outsider.

223
00:17:38,440 --> 00:17:40,460
The house was only a small matter.

224
00:17:40,460 --> 00:17:42,450
As for Ling Long, what are your plans?

225
00:17:42,450 --> 00:17:46,380
I just hate myself for

226
00:17:46,380 --> 00:17:50,580
not learning about business affairs from
my dad when he was alive.

227
00:17:50,580 --> 00:17:54,640
Otherwise it wouldn't be like now, with no ideas at all.

228
00:17:54,640 --> 00:17:56,960
All of the inventory and raw materials in the warehouse

229
00:17:56,960 --> 00:17:59,670
have been looted by the creditors.

230
00:17:59,670 --> 00:18:02,650
With Ling Long's situation right now,
I reckon there won't be any banks

231
00:18:02,650 --> 00:18:06,230
that would be willing to lend us money. But we still have Ling Long's factory.

232
00:18:06,230 --> 00:18:08,290
The workers are still here,

233
00:18:08,290 --> 00:18:11,190
and we still have Ling Long's sign.

234
00:18:11,190 --> 00:18:14,120
So, what does Brother Shao Tian mean?

235
00:18:14,120 --> 00:18:18,200
Since there is no way we can start operations to manufacture and we also owe so much debt,

236
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:21,850
how about, selling Ling Long first?

237
00:18:21,850 --> 00:18:26,040
After we pay off the debts, we can discuss
other matters at a later time.

238
00:18:26,040 --> 00:18:27,930
No.

239
00:18:31,340 --> 00:18:34,440
Ling Long was dad's lifetime of effort.

240
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:36,520
How could I sell it off?

241
